  {
   "question": "Where does Combat Rogue Phase 3 BiS come from?",
   "answer": "From the gear worn by 254 top-ranked Combat Rogue DPS parses on Warcraft Logs during Phase 3 (Black Temple and Mount Hyjal), aggregated per slot — what high parsers actually equip, not a spreadsheet ideal."
  },
  {
   "question": "What are the highest-consensus Combat Rogue items in Phase 3?",
   "answer": "Arcanite Steam-Pistol (89%), Edgewalker Longboots (88%), Drape of the Dark Reavers (82%). When an item sits above ~70% among top parsers, treat it as the priority drop to chase."
  },
  {
   "question": "Should I follow this list exactly for Phase 3?",
   "answer": "Use it as a loot-priority guide, not a checklist — expand each slot's alternatives, because second-choice items are often within a few percent and drop from entirely different bosses in Black Temple and Mount Hyjal."
